        <title>Regulator Valve (Oil Pressure)</title>
        <figure id="f3350010266" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figK13/K13004.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Regulator valve installation</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install two new O-rings on oil pressure regulator valve. Lubricate only bottom O-ring with
                clean engine oil.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install oil pressure regulator valve in the oil cooler housing and tighten to
                <hotlnk document="eges3351_246.xml" xrefid="t335001002" appearance="hottext">special torque</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="t335001002"/>.
            </para>
        </step1>
